Spider-Man;;67;;90;;PG-13;;"Spider-Man" centers on student Peter Parker (Tobey Maguire) who, after being bitten by a genetically-altered spider, gains superhuman strength and the spider-like ability to cling to any surface. He vows to use his abilities to fight crime, coming to understand the words of his beloved Uncle Ben: "With great power comes great responsibility.";;Fantasy,Action;;Sam Raimi;;2002;;Tobey Maguire,Willem Dafoe,Kirsten Dunst,James Franco,Cliff Robertson,Rosemary Harris,J.K. Simmons,Joe Manganiello,Gerry Becker,Bill Nunn,Jack Betts,Stanley Anderson,Ron Perkins;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderman